# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  credentials.env — 密碼類設定 / passwords & secrets
#  複製成 credentials.env 後填入（credentials.env 已被 .gitignore 忽略，永不入庫）
#  Copy to credentials.env and fill in (gitignored, never committed).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 統一管理員帳號（ADMIN_USER）在受管 Mac 上的 sudo 密碼。
# Homebrew 初次安裝、安裝 Command Line Tools 等需要。
# sudo password for the unified admin account on managed Macs (needed for Homebrew install, CLT, etc.)
ADMIN_SUDO_PASS=""

# ── 納管前的「既有帳號」（用於第一次透過 ARD/SSH 佈署金鑰；納管完成後可留空）──
# Existing account used for first-time onboarding via ARD/SSH before key-based access exists.
# Leave blank once onboarding is complete.
EXISTING_ADMIN_USER=""
EXISTING_ADMIN_PASS=""
EXISTING_ADMIN_SUDO_PASS=""
